data.description:
This FORMER MODEL ranch style home offers a Rate Buydown to help get your payments lower and is energy efficient with solar included!

For those seeking a quiet country life while still being close to the city & the easy freeway access is definitely a plus for those who enjoy weekend getaways to the mountains or exploring downtown Denver.

The "Aspen" Ranch Style Floorplan is absolutely stunning! With its 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, it provides ample space for comfortable living. The beautiful kitchen with energy-efficient appliances including gas stove, granite countertops, and recessed lighting is sure to impress. The spacious living room and dining room offer great areas for relaxation and entertaining.

The master suite with a walk-in closet is a great feature, providing privacy and convenience. The covered front porch adds to the curb appeal of the home and creates a welcoming entrance. It's also fantastic that this home is a former builder model, showcasing its quality and attention to detail.

The location of this home is prime, as it backs to open space and is situated in a low traffic area within the neighborhood. This allows for peaceful walks on nearby trails and the opportunity to enjoy breathtaking sunsets with loved ones. You will also love the park like large backyard for everyday fun and enjoyment! Imagine planting your own special garden here!

The professionally installed electric car charger in the garage is a fantastic addition for those who own electric vehicles and the size of this garage being 20x18 will also accommodate larger vehicles. In addition to the electric car charger this home comes with solar to help make it even more energy efficient!

As an added bonus, the new owner will receive an electric lawn mower and electric grass trimmer with the purchase of the home, making yard maintenance more convenient and environmentally friendly.

Call your agent to show you this lovely home today and let's make your dreams come true!
